MatchedSegment Contains the information about the linesegments (or subsegments) in other Features which match a given LineSegment.
MatchedShell The main data structure to represent the outer shell of a polygon that has been matched with one or more other polygons, and computed the adjusted version.

MatchedShellSubject A MatchedShell for features in the Subject dataset.
MatchedSubsegment Models the portion of a Subject segment which matches all or part of a segment in a Reference shell.
MatchedVertex A vertex of a shell which is within tolerance of another vertex.
SegmentMatcher A SegmentMatcher computes information about whether two boundary LineSegments match
SegmentProjecter Computes the projection of a target segment onto a reference segment.
